In the Intrastat Defaults page set the standard values to be associated with certain types of declarations:

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000367-0/18AdvIntrastatForItaly-en.PNG"><br>

| **Field**              | **Description**                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
|------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Type                   | Choose the Sales or Purchase side                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| Line Type              | Enter: <img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000367-0/19AdvIntrastatForItaly-en.PNG"><br>                                                                                                    |
| Document Type          | Choose between Invoice and Credit Memo                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
| Transaction Type       | Enter the code for the transaction type. In the list you can put the flag "triangular trade" for triangular trading operations, for which, in the EU trade file, the statistical values ??are reset                                                                                                                   |
| Transport Method       | choose the transport method                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
| County                 | Fill in the County                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| Entry/Exit point       | choose from the list of Intrastat forwarding codes. In this list you can assign your cost adjustment percentages (Cost Regulation %).                                                                                                                                                                               |
| Hide Statistical Value | the column related to the statistical value, in the declaration, is equal to zero                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| Hide Group Code        | if enabled the field is hidden in the declaration                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
| Supply Method          | indicates whether the service is provided in a single solution or in several times Å "I" code in the case where the service is delivered in a single solution; Å "R" code in the case where the service is delivered on several occasions. The value entered can still be modified in the lines of the Declaration. |